{"tid":2291771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"親身經歷理大戰役既人，有責任記低呢段歷史","createTime":"2020-11-19T04:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T05:11:37.000Z","uid":232848,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"701eb8c58481437f885520a89aa21684a661e841","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">《埋土一週年記》</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVNm7Ha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVNm7Ha.jpg&h=4366b7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AqLPVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AqLPVA.jpg&h=5867c980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事隔一年，終於可以慢慢回憶，記錄理大戰役。<br />\n<br />\n17號朝早，同隊友係A core十字路口會合後, 成朝keep住幾個鐘都係進進退退，當時攻勢並無中大戰咁誇張。最深印象係有2個望落去似form1/2既男女仔<br />\n<br />\n佢地企左係我地後面，得頭盔口罩，我行埋去叫佢地返去拎個豬嘴先好上黎，想幫手就照顧好自己先，連豬嘴都無行上前只會係送死。<br />\n<br />\n去到晏就4-5點，我去到後方尖東橋觀察情況，無錯就係裝甲車著火個條橋。當時衝突未有咁激烈，但係tg都不停係頭頂飛過。<br />\n<br />\n我一隻手拎住把遮掩護我隊友，突然間feel到額頭好似比人打左一拳咁，原來中左橡膠彈（因為本身入poly無諗住長留,所以無拎頭盔）但好彩既係，粒子彈首先打中左把遮再打中我額頭，所以把遮吸左好多力，而額頭都只係腫痛，唔死得。但如果粒子彈打中左我副泳鏡，我諗我隻眼應該就係咁先。<br />\n<br />\n18號朝早5點半，速龍同防暴全面由科學館攻入A core正門，我係A core平台，當時既我就黎體力不支，身邊既手足好多都無曬戰意，同埋個位因為太黑，所以基本上無記者會影到係咩環境。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">我既視線開始模糊，突然有數以百計既子彈由狗既方向向我地嘅方向掃射，一時間大家都反應唔到。</span><br />\n<br />\n慘叫聲夾雜住tg濃煙之下，我拎起旁邊張長檯做盾，係槍林彈雨入邊慢慢移動，身邊無數粒子彈飛過。當時接近全黑，<strong>所以根本分唔到係實彈，定係其他子彈</strong>，有啲打中左我張檯，成隻手震曬，有啲射中後面既玻璃，成個平台都充滿左玻璃碎裂既聲同槍聲。<br />\n<br />\n過左陣，喺科學館天台既狙擊手用槍嘅綠色laser照埋黎，戰火之下綠色特別顯眼。我不停向樓梯下面掉火魔，唔洗1分鐘，成條樓梯已經火光沖天，同時間全校既消防鐘都響緊。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，我開始覺得守唔住，係時候要搵方法走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkt_7/150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkt_7%2F150&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5lSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3eeb169d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkt_7/150</a><br />\n<br />\nHKT-7 deadbody字"},{"pid":"8a63040cab66b4523e0ac01d34702e12dc6c61b7","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed31c01ef9af1007a7dd10bc5db2e8f38d754e8","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1131f1d472d9e09db48df35a1f970fc317c4c4a7","tid":2291771,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b1290f80c7668bd8d0013368f4252f2237df1a8","tid":2291771,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1131f1d472d9e09db48df35a1f970fc317c4c4a7","tid":2291771,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"警察收料channel"},{"pid":"fbfc1a72cfb69048cc6601b9825ee27073966c93","tid":2291771,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3ff4e6147a02f2d0ae853e44d0110de3cd1414","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1131f1d472d9e09db48df35a1f970fc317c4c4a7","tid":2291771,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"可以起下我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff0bfdcafd35db499d6dc73a0b02a4746ed3b31","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46724f2bb087b76158449103a738b2bf779e167","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"係香港既手足就唔好學我啦"},{"pid":"9a100101e807052df3db5d7c5e216cc0d477c099","tid":2291771,"uid":54622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"巴打保重"},{"pid":"e68be3f84b6fae011b4a8f401bdb46420d0a51eb","tid":2291771,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"好多人未走出傷痛"},{"pid":"b361bfdf85a3d8db1f17880f99b0dc48992fec82","tid":2291771,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3ff4e6147a02f2d0ae853e44d0110de3cd1414","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1131f1d472d9e09db48df35a1f970fc317c4c4a7","tid":2291771,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"可以起下我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"你都唔好亂爆料<br />\n警察會用你既資料黎整好個故仔,告而家仲係香港既其他人"},{"pid":"0f6c3c7def978b045659d333dd2f3d72c65a88c2","tid":2291771,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"香港人點先肯移民 - 最完整分析<br />\n<br />\n1. 要大幅加人工<br />\n2. 要低稅過香港<br />\n3. 要保證一家大細,阿爸,阿媽,老婆,仔女,鄰居,同學,朋友, 全部無條件移民<br />\n4. 要同當地人福利體齊<br />\n5. 要有足夠錢係完全唔做野情況下生活5年以上<br />\n6. 要一移民就馬上置業<br />\n7. 要到當地維持香港生活模式<br />\n8. 要物價低過或同香港相約<br />\n9. 要大家移去同一個地區<br />\n10. 要當地人唔准歧視自己<br />\n11. 要識講流利英文同當地語言同方言<br />\n12. 要有專業技能, 如律師, 醫生等<br />\n13. 要住大城市<br />\n14. 要交通方便過香港<br />\n15. 要可以方便隨時來往香港<br />\n16. 要一落地就成為公民, 唔需要住 N 年或讀書等條件<br />\n17. 要有香港既食物選擇<br />\n18. 要附近冇其他國家新移民<br />\n19. 要當地一個中國人都冇<br />\n20. 要當地香港人全部都係黃絲<br />\n21. 要做非藍領既工作, 餐廳超市等一律唔做<br />\n22. 要上網快過香港<br />\n23. 要全家都同意移民先可以移民<br />\n24. 要至少有1000萬財產或本身有樓可賣<br />\n25. 要做太空人係香港繼續返工同時, 該國唔可以收稅, 又繼續畀戶籍你<br />\n26. 要返工唔可以辛苦過香港<br />\n27. 要娛樂多過香港<br />\n28. 要機場航班多過香港<br />\n29. 要方便去日本旅行<br />\n30. 要所有手足離港先走，共同進退<br />\n31. 要黃店一齊搬去外國<br />\n32. 要等大灣區發展，賺多十年錢先<br />\n33. 要等到升咗職做CEO先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n99. 要保證你出發前, 以上所有條件成立"},{"pid":"8fe1775014794ac19c16a87fdbbcd5a6204c9205","tid":2291771,"uid":67896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"對唔住 個日救唔到你地出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d46724f2bb087b76158449103a738b2bf779e167","tid":2291771,"uid":232848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"係香港既手足就唔好學我啦"}}